  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 1, 2025</p>

  <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Michael Norton's n8n Service</strong> ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and protects any personal information that you provide when using our application.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information</strong> (such as name, email address) when explicitly provided by you</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data</strong> (such as IP address, browser type, and usage logs) to help us improve our service</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
    <li>Authenticate users</li>
    <li>Communicate with users when necessary</li>
    <li>Ensure security and compliance with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell or rent your personal information. We may share your data only:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>With your consent</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    <li>With service providers bound by confidentiality agreements</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.</p>

  <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>Our application may use third-party services (such as Google APIs) that are governed by their own privacy policies. We recommend reviewing those policies.</p>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Access and update your personal information</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent where applicable</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Effective Date."</p>

